<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 00:50:04 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>大众汽车与小鹏汽车签署协议开发两款 B 级电池电动汽车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-xpeng-ink-deal-develop-two-b-class-battery-evs-2024-02-29/</link><description>德国汽车制造商大众汽车和中国电动汽车制造商小鹏汽车周四表示，已达成协议，联合开发两款 B 级电池电动汽车。</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 00:29:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-xpeng-ink-deal-develop-two-b-class-battery-evs-2024-02-29/</guid></item><item><title>商务部长表示中方愿加强与埃及的经贸合作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-willing-enhance-economic-trade-cooperation-with-egypt-commerce-minister-2024-02-28/</link><description>中国商务部援引中国商务部部长的话说，中方愿进一步促进与埃及的经贸合作，继续鼓励和支持中国企业赴埃投资兴业。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 23:34:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-willing-enhance-economic-trade-cooperation-with-egypt-commerce-minister-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>论文称加拿大因与北京分享信息而解雇了两名科学家</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/canada-fired-two-scientists-sharing-information-with-beijing-says-paper-2024-02-28/</link><description>据《环球邮报》周三报道，加拿大于 2021 年解雇了两名在高度安全的传染病实验室工作的科学家，因为他们向中国提供了机密信息。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 22:11:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/canada-fired-two-scientists-sharing-information-with-beijing-says-paper-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>早间竞价：聚光灯聚焦日本、澳大利亚消费者</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-02-28/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 21:48:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>北京将举办2027年世锦赛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/athletics/beijing-host-2027-world-championships-2024-02-28/</link><description>世界田径管理机构周三表示，北京已被选为举办 2027 年世界田径锦标赛。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 20:11:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/athletics/beijing-host-2027-world-championships-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国汽车制造商比亚迪高管表示正在寻找墨西哥工厂选址</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-carmaker-byd-launches-low-cost-dolphin-mini-ev-mexico-2024-02-28/</link><description>比亚迪美洲公司首席执行官斯特拉·李周三对路透社表示，中国电动汽车制造商比亚迪正在墨西哥寻找建厂地点，旨在提高该公司在当地市场的份额。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 18:30:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-carmaker-byd-launches-low-cost-dolphin-mini-ev-mexico-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>美国贸易负责人本周排除了世贸组织争端解决方案，但表示情绪积极</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-trade-chief-rules-out-wto-dispute-deal-this-week-says-mood-is-positive-2024-02-28/</link><description>美国贸易代表凯瑟琳·戴周三排除了本周就世贸组织争端解决上诉改革达成协议的可能性，但表示世贸组织就此问题的谈判是积极的，并显示出一些进展。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 16:22:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-trade-chief-rules-out-wto-dispute-deal-this-week-says-mood-is-positive-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>Polestar 融资近 10 亿美元，预计 2024 年利润率将有所改善</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/polestar-raises-almost-1-bln-sees-margins-improving-2024-2024-02-28/</link><description>Polestar周三表示，已从银行财团筹集了9.5亿美元贷款，有助于填补沃尔沃汽车表示将停止向这家电动汽车制造商提供资金后留下的资金缺口，导致其在纽约上市的股价上涨18.5%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 14:22:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/polestar-raises-almost-1-bln-sees-margins-improving-2024-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>印度和南非在世贸组织谈判中阻止重大投资协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india-south-africa-block-investment-deal-wto-talks-2024-02-28/</link><description>印度和南非在阿布扎比举行的世界贸易组织会议上正式反对一项投资协议，阻止该协议的通过，观察人士称此举可能会阻碍数千亿美元的投资。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 14:21:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india-south-africa-block-investment-deal-wto-talks-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>ATP与沙特阿拉伯PIF签署多年战略合作伙伴关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/atp-signs-multi-year-strategic-partnership-with-saudi-arabias-pif-2024-02-28/</link><description>男子网球管理机构周三表示，ATP巡回赛和沙特阿拉伯公共投资基金（PIF）已经签署了一项多年战略合作伙伴关系，此举凸显了这个海湾国家对全球体育运动日益增长的影响力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 14:08:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/atp-signs-multi-year-strategic-partnership-with-saudi-arabias-pif-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>印度在世贸组织会议上寻求农业和争端制度改革</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-seeks-reforms-agriculture-disputes-system-wto-meeting-2024-02-28/</link><description>印度贸易部长周三表示，印度希望本周在阿布扎比举行的高级别会议上就农业改革的关键内容以及恢复世界贸易组织的仲裁权达成协议。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 14:01:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-seeks-reforms-agriculture-disputes-system-wto-meeting-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>意大利与特斯拉和中国汽车制造商洽谈寻找第二家汽车生产商</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italy-talks-tesla-others-search-second-carmaker-2024-02-28/</link><description>意大利工业部长周三表示，意大利一直在与特斯拉和三家中国汽车制造商进行谈判，试图吸引另一家制造商并实现 130 万辆汽车的年产量目标。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 13:53:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italy-talks-tesla-others-search-second-carmaker-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>美国共和党参议员希望提高对中国汽车的关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/republican-senator-wants-hike-tariffs-chinese-vehicles-2024-02-28/</link><description>美国共和党参议员乔什·霍利周三提出立法，提高对中国汽车进口的关税，因为人们越来越担心这对美国汽车公司的潜在竞争影响。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 12:06:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/republican-senator-wants-hike-tariffs-chinese-vehicles-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国总理李克强敦促加强与美国的经贸关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/chinas-premier-li-urges-stronger-economic-trade-ties-with-us-2024-02-28/</link><description>据中国国家广播电台报道，中国国务院总理李强周三在会见来访的美国代表团时表示，中美应加强经贸关系，华盛顿应避免与中国脱钩。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 11:36:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/chinas-premier-li-urges-stronger-economic-trade-ties-with-us-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：美国增长 3% 以上；苹果降档，新西兰惊喜</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-02-28/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 11:02:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-02-28/</guid></item></channel></rss>